Interface IMeteredUsageListener


  • public interface IMeteredUsageListener
    This interface represents a listener for receiving MeteredUsageNotification. The class that is interested in processing MeteredUsageNotification should implement this interface.

    Notes: This interface is place holder only and not yet supported by Smart Licensing.
